data.description: Stunning, Immaculate, And Exquisite! From Your First Step Into The Foyer, You Will Be Amazed At The Spacious, Open Feel Of This Gorgeous Home. The Living Room Is Accented With A Gas Fireplace, Recessed Lighting And Multiple Windows. The Kitchen Is Adorned With Beautiful Cabinetry, Appliances That Stay, (new Dw '23) And Peaceful Views Of The Large Back Yard. The Formal Dining Room Boasts A Bay Window, Adding Elegance To The Home. The Laundry Room And A Half-bath Complete The Main Level. Upstairs You Will Find 4 Nice Sized Bedrooms (one With New Vinyl Flooring), A Huge Bonus Room, And Two Full Bathrooms. The Full Basement Provides Extra Storage. The New Ac Unit ('22) And A New Hw Heater ('23) Add Peace Of Mind To Your Home Ownership. Outside, Enjoy Lounging On The Deck, Relaxing On The Fenced Patio In Front Of Your Firepit, And Swimming In Your Above Ground Pool (new Pump/sand Filter '22'). *all Measurements Are Approximations* *some Wall Colors Rendered By Photographer*
